Use New Memory Function Calls To Get Extended Memory

If the BIOS supports it, there are two additional functions which
return the size of extended memory in kilobytes, this time handling >
64 MB.

MAKEFILE	Make sensitive to LNKCMD environment variable.

MEM_MAIN.ASM	In CHECK_PHYS, try the extended memory functions
		  0DA88h and 0E801h.

